sw5cZPrXg">Khiếu Năng Tĩnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-Lan-T%C3%ADnh-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/Kim-l%C5%A9-kh%C3%BAc-T%E1%BA%B7ng-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ph%E1%BA%A7n/poem-tWf_zs6AGhkbCEHWty5jkw">Kim lũ khúc - Tặng Lương Phần - 金縷曲－贈梁汾</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-Lan-T%C3%ADnh-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c/author-4UIcOQq3X5B-YNUldGF_5g">Nạp Lan Tính Đức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-%C4%90%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-huy%E1%BB%87n-Ng%C3%B4-th%E1%BA%ADp-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-giang-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-tr%E1%BA%A1ch/poem-b69cDggbtgVsdx4YW4pmOA">Lưỡng Đương huyện Ngô thập thị ngự giang thượng trạch - 兩當縣吳十侍禦江上宅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Minh-Thi%E1%BB%87n/T%C3%A1-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A1ng-S%C6%A1n-s%E1%BB%A9-Giao-xu%C3%A2n-d%E1%BA%A1-quan-k%E1%BB%B3-t%E1%BA%B7ng-th%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-G_GjLa3wwtWwOpKhdh1DGA">Tá Lưỡng Sơn sứ Giao xuân dạ quan kỳ tặng thế tử - 佐兩山使交春夜觀棋贈世子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Minh-Thi%E1%BB%87n/author-x8idisv6NjB3rqg1B7NULw">Từ Minh Thiện</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%AB-b%E1%BB%99/poem-7Jnq1UO-yGNm5G2tG3F9cA">Từ bộ - 徐步</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
